&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Careers at Yoodli&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We’re on a mission to help people communicate with confidence&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yoodli is an AI-powered experiential learning platform that uses AI roleplays to personalize real-life practice and transform how organizations learn and prepare. We’re pioneering a new category, AI Roleplays, because we believe nobody should miss out on the opportunities they deserve because of how they communicate. Static content doesn’t create behavior change. Practice does.&lt;/p&gt;
